        <!-- Website Overview Section -->
        <div class="section">
    <h1>Welcome to MOVIE NERDS</h1>
    <p>
        MOVIE NERDS is an online platform where movie lovers and TV show enthusiasts come together to share insights, opinions, and engage in thoughtful discussions. Whether you're a fan of the latest blockbuster, a classic film aficionado, or an indie film buff, this community is for you. We aim to provide a safe, respectful, and enjoyable environment for all members, where your passion for movies can flourish.
    </p>
    <p>
        **We value your privacy and the security of your data.** Any personal information you share with us, including your display name and any interactions on the platform, is securely stored and protected. We do not sell or share your data with third parties, ensuring your privacy remains intact while you enjoy our community.
    </p>
    <p>
        **Weekly Movie Discussions:** Each week, we feature a curated selection of movies and TV shows that form the basis of our community discussions. These selections are chosen to cater to a wide range of tastes, ensuring there's always something new and exciting to talk about.
    </p>
    <p>
        **Discussion Section:** In the discussion section, you'll find detailed overviews of the movies and shows being discussed that week. This section is your go-to place for in-depth conversations, where you can share your thoughts, theories, and critiques with fellow movie nerds.
    </p>
    <p>
        **Announcements Section:** The announcements section is where we keep you updated with the latest news and new features on our platform. From upcoming movie releases to special events and new discussion topics, this section ensures you're always in the loop.
    </p>
    <p>
        **Trusted Sources:** Our discussion topics are sourced from trusted, reputable sources to ensure accuracy and relevance. We strive to provide you with reliable information that enhances your viewing experience and sparks meaningful conversations.
    </p>
    <p>
        **Spoiler Alert:** Please be aware that our discussions often delve into plot details, twists, and endings. We encourage you to participate in discussions with caution if you have not yet watched the movies or shows being discussed to avoid spoilers.
    </p>
</div>
        <!-- How to Use the Website Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>How to Use MOVIE NERDS</h2>
            <p>
                To join the conversation and contribute to the discussions, follow these simple steps:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Create a Display Name:</strong> Start by creating a display name that uniquely identifies you in the community.</li>
                <li><strong>Display Name Requirements:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The display name must be at least four characters long.</li>
                        <li>It should only contain letters (A-Z) and up to two numbers (0-9).</li>
                        <li>The numbers can either appear at the beginning or end of the name.</li>
                        <li>Special characters (e.g., commas, periods, or symbols) are not allowed.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Join the Chat:</strong> Once you've created a valid display name, click the "Start Chat" button to join the discussion.</li>
                <li><strong>Engage Respectfully:</strong> Participate in the conversations, share your thoughts on movies and TV shows, and respect the opinions of others.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                By adhering to these guidelines, you help maintain the positive atmosphere that makes MOVIE NERDS a great place for movie fans.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Rules and Regulations Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Rules and Regulations</h2>
            <p>
                To ensure a safe and welcoming environment for all, we ask that you follow these rules and regulations while using the MOVIE NERDS platform:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Respectful Communication:</strong> All users are expected to communicate respectfully. Inappropriate or rude behavior will not be tolerated.</li>
                <li><strong>No Explicit Content:</strong> Sharing explicit content, including nudity, is strictly prohibited.</li>
                <li><strong>Privacy and Anonymity:</strong> Do not share personal information about yourself or others. Users should avoid addressing each other by their real names.</li>
                <li><strong>Character References:</strong> When discussing movie characters, refrain from using their actual names to maintain the integrity of the discussion.</li>
                <li><strong>No Spamming:</strong> Spamming or flooding the chat with repetitive messages is not allowed.</li>
                <li><strong>Prohibited Language:</strong> Hateful, discriminatory, or abusive language will result in immediate removal from the community.</li>
                <li><strong>No Advertising:</strong> Advertising products, services, or self-promotion is not allowed on this platform.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                By following these rules, you help us maintain a community that is inclusive, respectful, and enjoyable for everyone.
            </p>
        </div>

